   // =============================================================================
// Function Class: Show/Hide product promotions &amp; special offers link
// =============================================================================

function showElement(id) {
  var elm = document.getElementById(id);
  if (elm) {
    elm.style.visibility = 'visible';
    if (elm.getAttribute('name') == 'heroQuickPromoDiv') {
      elm.style.display = 'block';
    }
  }
}
function hideElement(id) {
  var elm = document.getElementById(id);
  if (elm) {
    elm.style.visibility = 'hidden';
    if (elm.getAttribute('name') == 'heroQuickPromoDiv') {
      elm.style.display = 'none';
    }
  }
}
function showHideElement(h_id, div_id) {
  var hiddenTag = document.getElementById(h_id);
  if (hiddenTag) {
    showElement(div_id);
  } else {
    hideElement(div_id);
  }
}

		    }
		return exception;
           	}
		i++;
	    }
        }
	return null;
    }

	    }
	}

	}
        return false;
    }

A   U   I   _   B   U   I   L   D   _   D   A   T   E   )       {   P   .   w   h   e   n   (   '   c   f   '   ,       '   A   '   )   .   e   x   e   c   u   t   e   (   e   x   e   c   u   t   e   S   c   r   i   p   t   )   ;       }   e   l   s   e       i   f       (   t   y   p   e   o   f   (   a   m   z   n   J   Q   )       !   =   =       "   u   n   d   e   f   i   n   e   d   "   )       {   a   m   z   n   J   Q   .   o   n   C   o   m   p   l   e   t   i   o   n   (   '   a   m   z   n   J   Q   .   c   r   i   t   i   c   a   l   F   e   a   t   u   r   e   '   ,       e   x   e   c   u   t   e   S   c   r   i   p   t   )   ;   }   }   )   (   w   i   n   d   o   w   ,       d   o   c   u   m   e   n   t   )   ;   /   s   c   r   i   p   t   &gt;
